FROM sa_inoutput AS io
LEFT JOIN sa_inoutput_item AS io_item ON io_item.inoutput_id = io.id
LEFT JOIN chi_product AS p ON io_item.product_id = p.id
WHERE io.STATUS="cancelled_wo_out_products"
AND io.create_time > '2019-02-07'
AND io.method != 'not_order'
AND io.re_in_type IN ("out_of_stock", "not_product")
AND io.source ='chiaki.vn'

GROUP BY io_item.product_code
ORDER BY count_io desc
